<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Foodie Hub</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            background: #fffaf5;
            color: #333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b00, #ff9f43);
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #222;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 90vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 60px 8%;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255,107,0,0.08), rgba(255,159,67,0.08));
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-text {
            max-width: 520px;
            animation: slideLeft 1.2s ease;
        }

        .hero-text h2 {
            font-size: 52px;
            color: #ff6b00;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .hero-text p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .hero-buttons a {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            background: #ff6b00;
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-right: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(255,107,0,0.3);
        }

        .hero-buttons a:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.03);
            background: #e45c00;
        }

        .hero-image {
            animation: floatImage 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .hero-image img {
            width: 420px;
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 60px 20px 25px;
        }

        .section-title h2 {
            font-size: 38px;
            color: #ff6b00;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .section-title p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 17px;
        }

        .menu {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 28px;
            padding: 30px 8% 60px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 18px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            transition: transform 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
            animation: fadeUp 1s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
        }

        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .card-content {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card-content h3 {
            color: #ff6b00;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .card-content p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #222;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #ff6b00;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #e45c00;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px 8% 70px;
        }

        .feature-box {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .feature-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
        }

        .feature-box h3 {
            color: #ff6b00;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            background: #222;
            color: white;
            padding: 22px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        @keyframes slideLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-40px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(35px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes floatImage {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .hero {
                text-align: center;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 30px;
            }

            .hero-text h2 {
                font-size: 38px;
            }

            header {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            nav a {
                margin: 0 8px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>🍔 Foodie Hub</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="#home">Home</a>
            <a href="#menu">Menu</a>
            <a href="#features">Why Us</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h2>Delicious Food, Delivered Fast</h2>
            <p>
                Experience fresh burgers, cheesy pizzas, creamy pasta and more.
                Designed as a modern food ordering homepage for your DevOps Docker project.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="#menu">Explore Menu</a>
                <a href="#features">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504674900247-0877df9cc836?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="Food Banner">
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-title" id="menu">
        <h2>Our Best Sellers</h2>
        <p>Freshly prepared meals crafted for taste and speed.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="menu">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568901346375-23c9450c58cd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Burger">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Cheese Burger</h3>
                <p>Juicy grilled patty with cheese, lettuce and our special sauce.</p>
                <div class="price">₹149</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Order Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513104890138-7c749659a591?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Pizza">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Italian Pizza</h3>
                <p>Loaded with cheese, olives, herbs and fresh toppings.</p>
                <div class="price">₹249</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Order Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621996346565-e3dbc646d9a9?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Pasta">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>White Sauce Pasta</h3>
                <p>Creamy pasta with herbs, vegetables and rich white sauce.</p>
                <div class="price">₹199</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Order Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-title" id="features">
        <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
        <p>Better food experience with smooth UI and faster delivery feel.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>⚡ Fast Delivery</h3>
            <p>Quick order flow with a clean and user-friendly experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>🍽 Fresh Food</h3>
            <p>High-quality dishes prepared with fresh ingredients.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>🎨 Modern Design</h3>
            <p>Attractive visuals, animations, and responsive card-based layout.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 Foodie Hub | DevOps Project by Asad</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
